summary: Adds Psiijic Robes and these gauntlets I found that i believe were meant to be part of the last Collage of Winterhold quest I just renamed them. Can be found in the Alchemists Shack on the back roads of Helgen through the mountains.
descriptionHtml:
Adds Psiijic Robes and these gauntlets I found that i believe were meant to be part of the last Collage of Winterhold quest I just renamed them. Can be found in the Alchemists Shack on the back roads of Helgen through the mountains.

PSIIJIC-
robes, gauntlets, boots, hood
WARLOCK GLOVES-
warlock gloves
author: DemonLord7654
